title: LOAD_RESOURCE_FILE
content:
0x76A9EE1F// LoadResourceFile
char* LOAD_RESOURCE_FILE(char* resourceName, char* fileName);Parameters:resourceName: The resource name.fileName: The file in the resource.Returns: The file contentsReads the contents of a text file in a specified resource.
If executed on the client, this file has to be included in files in the resource manifest.
Example: local data = LoadResourceFile("devtools", "data.json")
